<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM1.9.2">
<l>kiṅkiṇikaṭṭik kiṟikaṭṭi kaiyiṉil</l>
<l>kaṅkaṇamiṭṭuk kaḻuttiltoṭarkaṭṭi</l>
<l>taṉkaṇattālē catirānaṭantuvan</l>
<l>teṉkaṇṇaṉeṉṉaippuṟampulkuvāṉ</l>
<l rend="indent">empirāṉeṉṉaippuṟampulkuvāṉ.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Wearing tinkling anklets [and] a coral bracelet,</l>
<l>putting bangles on [His] hands,</l>
<l>[and] wearing a chain on [His] neck,</l>
<l>my Kaṇṇaṉ, having come walking gracefully</l>
<l>with the collection of them,</l>
<l>will embrace me [from] behind;</l>
<l>my Lord will embrace me [from] behind.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
